EN: Whenever I feel lonely, I find a good book to pass the time.

ZH: 每当大雨来临，我就会打开窗户听雨声。
EN: Whenever there is heavy rain, I open the window and listen to the sound of rain.

ZH: 每当我没时间做饭，我会叫外卖。
EN: Whenever I don't have time to cook, I order takeout.

ZH: 每当朋友来访，我都会煮一些美味的菜招待他们。
EN: Whenever friends visit, I always cook some delicious dishes to treat them.

